author: stsp
msg: * tools/dev/unix/build/Makefile.svn: Allow my custom build script, and by
extension the OpenBSD buildbot, to build SVN's dependencies in parallel.
This requires declaring build dependencies properly, and also clearing
MAKEFLAGS when invoking 'make' in subjobs, because in parallel mode GNU
make mode puts flags into MAKEFLAGS which BSD make doesn't like.
